messages.message:
Hi all, I was doing the regression API test design and testing it on Instabase. But due one destructive test, it's broke my subspace explorer page ("my-repo" subspace). Anyone know how can I fix it?
The details are here: https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/SDET-58
From now on I'll do this type of testing on dogfood. Sorry for the inconvenience. I'll make sure from the next time to not perform any negative testing on prod.
have you tried making an API call to delete the folder with an empty name?
also cc <!subteam^S01DXHX6FPT> to block folder names containing just a space when validating file paths
Thanks, Serena. I'll try with delete API and will check if it's fixed or not.
